{"tid":2066481,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北韓炸毀南北韓聯絡辦公室","createTime":"2020-06-16T10:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T10:09:20.000Z","uid":127469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"482342c2ac789ba4eb255e9d683ac2b076c9fed7","tid":2066481,"uid":127469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"南韓統一部證實，北韓將位於北韓邊境的開城工業園區的兩韓聯絡辦公室炸毀。韓聯社報道，開城工業園下午傳來一聲爆炸巨響及傳出煙霧。<br />\n<br />\n南北韓關係近日迅速惡化，北韓以南韓在邊境地區發放傳單為由，關閉雙方的聯絡渠道，並將對韓事務改為「對敵行動」。北韓人民軍總參謀部表示，將於南北韓的非軍事地區，重新部署兵力，並向韓方散發傳單。勞動黨第一副部長金與正早前表示，不久的將來韓方將看到毫無用處的聯絡辦公室變成廢墟的情景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532361-20200616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532361-20200616.htm&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=815be50a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532361-20200616.htm&h=5b9bce32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532361-20200616.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中印、兩韓⋯⋯  歐美亂完又到亞洲亂 <br />\n2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65fccbc155ea645d5120caa5547011d70a39f30","tid":2066481,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343f215798d32292c4b5672cc1df4506b6872647","tid":2066481,"uid":346003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n<br />\n[突發][活動]六點IFC和你唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2066468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2066468</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"efa4794b981a7905a0bef5f6bf557b2167c45bfa","tid":2066481,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"WW3 coming soon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk